title: Stefan Ninčić
text:
Stefan Ninčić (<a href="Serbian%20Cyrillic">Serbian Cyrillic</a>: Стефан Нинчић; born 5 November 1991, in <a href="Smederevo">Smederevo</a>) is a <a href="Serbia">Serbia</a>n <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who plays for <a href="FK%20Smederevo">FK Smederevo</a> in the <a href="Serbian%20SuperLiga">Serbian SuperLiga</a>.
He made his professional debut on 5 May 2012, in Serbian SuperLiga match versus <a href="FK%20Spartak%20Zlatibor%20Voda">Spartak Subotica</a>.
